          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The system resolves the table view style in the following manner:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "unorderedList",
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "If the table view is in a sidebar split-view controller item, "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableview/3622474-effectivestyle"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " resolves to "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableviewstyle/nstableviewstylesourcelist"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "If the tableâ€™s scroll view has a border, "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableview/3622474-effectivestyle"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " resolves to "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableviewstyle/nstableviewstylefullwidth"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Otherwise "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableview/3622474-effectivestyle"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " resolves to "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableviewstyle/nstableviewstyleinset"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": ". However, if the table needs extra space to fit its column cells, "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableview/3622474-effectivestyle"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " resolves to "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableviewstyle/nstableviewstylefullwidth"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "aside",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "For backward compatibility reasons, when "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableview/1526311-selectionhighlightstyle"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " is set to "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableviewselectionhighlightstyle/nstableviewselectionhighlightstylesourcelist"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": false,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstableview/3622475-style"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " also resolves to "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
